These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, software-developer, writer, fisherman, musician, chef, doctor
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, polish, british, dutch, italian, spanish
 1. the fisherman is on the left of the british##1
 2. the dutch is the fisherman##1
 3. the doctor is on the right of the chef##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the italian##1
 5. the writer is in the middle##1
 6. the japanese is on the far left##1
 7. the musician is the japanese##1
 8. the bartender is on the right of the italian##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the brazilian##1
10. the british is on the left of the writer##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | musician | fisherman | software-developer | writer | bartender | chef | doctor |
| Nationality   | japanese    | dutch   | british      | italian | polish    | brazilian    | spanish         |

