.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: kiwi, lettuce, lime, banana, apple, blueberry, onion
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, dubstep, trance, ambient, indie, r&b
 1. the fan of ambient is the person eating banana##1
 2. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 7. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 9. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating lime##1
10. the person eating banana is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | kiwi | lettuce | apple | banana | blueberry | onion | lime |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | dubstep   | trance   | ambient      | hip-hop       | r&b       | indie     |

