.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: cabbage, broccoli, grapes, watermelon, apricot, avocado, cranberry
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, nurse, videographer, project-manager, electrician, accountant, entrepreneur
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person eating apricot is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 3. the nurse is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the dressmaker is the person eating apricot##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the nurse##1
 7. the nurse is on the left of the videographer##1
 8. the nurse is on the right of the project-manager##1
 9. the person eating avocado is the project-manager##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the dressmaker##1
11. the project-manager is in the middle##1
12. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | broccoli | apricot     | grapes  | avocado       | cabbage       | cranberry  | watermelon   |
| Job    | accountant  | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | nurse | videographer | electrician |

