.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, funk, reggae, techno, classical, pop, trance
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, mexican, japanese, polish, malaysian, german
 1. the fan of classical is the colombian##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 3. the malaysian is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the malaysian##1
 9. the fan of reggae is the polish##1
10. the polish is on the left of the fan of funk##1
11. the german is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | trance     | techno     | reggae      | funk | classical      | electronic     |
| Nationality   | japanese | mexican | malaysian | polish | german | colombian | canadian |

