.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, puzzles, chess, woodworking, skydiving, photography
7 different pets are kept: pony, goat, hedgehog, rat, bird, chinchilla, mouse
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | puzzles | skydiving     | chess | photography | woodworking | camping |
| Pet     | mouse   | hedgehog    | bird | chinchilla     | pony         | rat     | goat        |

