.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, tea, lemonade
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike, car, snowmobile, train, airplane, helicopter
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | fanta | tea   | mirinda | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | milk | cola |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | train | taxi | airplane     | motorbike | helicopter | car   |

