.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, family, documentary, action, scientific, comedy, romance
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, train, bus, ship, taxi, airplane, bike
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the van is the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | romance | action | scientific | comedy     | family | documentary |
| Transport     | airplane | ship      | bike | bus    | taxi | train   | van  |

