 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
